1955;;Francis in the Navy;;American;;Arthur Lubin;;Donald O'Connor, Martha Hyer;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Francis_in_the_Navy;;U. S. Army officer Lt. Peter Sterling gets mistaken for his lookalike in the U. S. Navy, Bosun's Mate 'Slicker' Donevan, and as a result gets promptly shipped to Donevan's base. With his old pal Francis, Sterling continues his military career misadventures, this time in the Navy.